add/remove a route
=========================
ip route del 192.168.46.79/32


add static route
==========================
internal network example:
ip route add 10.0.0.0/8 via 10.200.0.130 dev eth1
								^ip on eth1

add ip
======
ip addr add 192.168.60.1/24 dev br0


magic 169.254 bullshit
==========================
ip addr show dev br0 scope global
